title: (Tues Full Show) Bobby Friend Talked to Chris Rock Yesterday + Lunchbox Calls to Claim His Oscars Goodie Bag
itunes:title: (Tues Full Show) Bobby Friend Talked to Chris Rock Yesterday + Lunchbox Calls to Claim His Oscars Goodie Bag
description:
We talk about the updates on the Will Smith + Chris Rock Oscar moment. Bobby’s friend has inside info after talking to Chris Rock yesterday. We also debate whether we think now if it was real or not. Lunchbox decided to call the Oscars lost and found claiming he left his bag there…
